		<title>Digital Nomads: Amara Uyanna has worked across four continents. She is not done.</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/04/25/digital-nomads-how-amara-uyanna-built-a-global-career/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Eme Oreoluwa]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 14:48:29 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Digital Nomads]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Al Jazeera]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Amara Uyanna]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[ExxonMobil]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Lazerpay]]></category>
